program name:
	Smart Home Inspector 
	(executable name: shi)

what it does:
	inspects log files from smart home hubs and displays the events in them in a video interface

how to install:
	
	requires... 
		C++ 11 or higher 
		GTK+ 3.0 or higher
		the latest version of the Make utility

	navigate to the project folder in the command line and enter "make install" with root permissions. SHI will then be installed to the /usr/local/bin directory. 
